            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Google sources Knowledge Graph data from Wikipedia, Wikidata, the CIA World Factbook, licensed databases, and the broader web. Organization schema (JSON-LD) on your own website — especially with sameAs links — helps Google match your web presence to your Knowledge Graph entity record.</p></div></div>
